fields.bio: As a record store owner and collector, I am immersed in the world of vinyl on a daily basis. I curate a diverse selection of records for my customers, and enjoy discovering new artists and labels. When not running my store, I enjoy attending record fairs and conventions.

I enjoy sharing my passion for records with others through writing and social media. I collect records from different eras and genres, and love to research the stories behind them. In my spare time, I enjoy attending record release parties and organizing listening clubs.

I am always on the hunt for rare vinyl and obscure releases. I love digging through crates at record stores and flea markets, and expanding my collection. When not listening to music, I enjoy reading about the history of different genres and artists.
